pull_request.title: Restructured appointment process
pull_request.body:
This pull request introduces several changes to enhance navigation, refactor components, and improve code maintainability in the physician and appointment-related modules. The key updates include adding navigation functionality in the `Physician` page, creating a reusable `AppointmentCard` component, and replacing inline appointment management logic with a dedicated `AppointmentTable` component.

### Navigation Enhancements:
* Added the `useNavigate` hook to the `Physician` page and implemented navigation for "View all appointments" and "View all patients" buttons to their respective routes (`/doctor/appointments` and `/doctor/patients`). (`[[1]](diffhunk://#diff-cbf98c16a1e153c6b9add1101f3c8b1078e7b3f7d2da9fd69399577b093a0e62R2)`, `[[2]](diffhunk://#diff-cbf98c16a1e153c6b9add1101f3c8b1078e7b3f7d2da9fd69399577b093a0e62R27)`, `[[3]](diffhunk://#diff-cbf98c16a1e153c6b9add1101f3c8b1078e7b3f7d2da9fd69399577b093a0e62L271-R273)`, `[[4]](diffhunk://#diff-cbf98c16a1e153c6b9add1101f3c8b1078e7b3f7d2da9fd69399577b093a0e62L319-R321)`)

### Component Refactoring:
* Extracted the appointment card logic from `AppointmentList` into a new reusable `AppointmentCard` component, improving modularity and reusability. (`[src/components/appointment-card/AppointmentCard.tsxR1-R62](diffhunk://#diff-bdbf787e3d9b747b952b5cea3962baceed0dea0888f2605d46ddac0b081fbc63R1-R62)`)
* Replaced inline appointment management logic in `AppointmentList` with the `AppointmentTable` component, simplifying the structure and enabling better separation of concerns. (`[[1]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L34-R33)`, `[[2]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L271-R226)`)

### Code Cleanup and Maintenance:
* Removed redundant imports and unused code in `AppointmentList` and `AppointmentTable` files, streamlining the codebase. (`[[1]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L2-R2)`, `[[2]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L13-R15)`, `[[3]](diffhunk://#diff-8a5bf2568c8dd277ac9de78ad9175c0810d70598a575c2c856c7b92d8a571676L1-L21)`, `[[4]](diffhunk://#diff-8a5bf2568c8dd277ac9de78ad9175c0810d70598a575c2c856c7b92d8a571676R11-R20)`)
* Fixed minor formatting issues, such as consistent use of trailing commas in object literals. (`[[1]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L56-R55)`, `[[2]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L74-R73)`, `[[3]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L92-R91)`, `[[4]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L110-R109)`, `[[5]](diffhunk://#diff-83ebb5d63ef5a1eb7553f53e3db7533444e5f9a77159d36a407e7b096319b468L128-R139)`)
